title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Ben Leber/Matt Birk
description: Nordo fills in for PA on Day 4 of Vocal Maintenance. He talks Zach Parise getting benched against Vegas last night, a new rule in the NFL, and Vikings free agency. Ben Leber joins to talk Vikings and massages, and Matt Birk joins to talk NFL and Vikings moving forward.
